text:
(Before It's News)
Please send donations sponsoring us for every skydive. Make your check out to “ New Salem Baptist Church ” and send to: 173 Olde Farm Rd
Pittsboro NC 27312
Donations will go to Helping Hands Ministry Pakistan to purchase new sewing machines for impoverished Christian women with children. This creates self-employment and income for their families.
